<br>
Personally, the expressions look intensely passionate but not violent to me.  However, I have the following liabilities in my life that prevent me from getting as accurate a perspective as others here:<br>
<br>
I am not gay, and I am not an elf -- but mind you, some of my best friends are elves.  I do not have green hair (at the moment), and I am not clean-shaven.  I also find it difficult and tiresome to get distressed over unusual sexual relationships that contain something other than a man and a woman having unadorned, ordinary sex.  <br>
<br>
So all of that, especially the elf thing, makes me woefully unqualified to tell what those two are doing, and which one of them is having fun, and whether the other one is not having fun.  I wish Giovanni would have them hold signs explaining what they are thinking at the moment.<br>
<br>
Compared to sea otters mating, something that oddly enough I *have* seen a couple of times, the signature looks pretty tame.  I think we really ought to refocus our considerable energy here on the otters, and teach them to draw less blood and be more considerate of their mate's feelings.<br>
